parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the trailer brake system can cause loss of control, accidents, and potentially lead to serious injuries or fatalities, especially when towing heavy trailers.
symptoms: The trailer brakes fail to engage
the trailer brakes stop working after a random period of time
the trailer brakes fail to work after sitting in traffic
the trailer brakes can be restored temporarily by removing and reinstalling fuse #62 in the under-hood fuse box.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the trailer electrical system can cause the trailer lights, turn signals, stop lights, and warning lights to be very dim or not visible, which can lead to accidents or collisions, especially when changing lanes or braking.
symptoms: and warning lights on the left side are very dim or not visible
the lights work properly when the trailer is initially hooked up but fail intermittently while driving
error messages such as "Trailer Left Turn Lamps Fault Check Lamps" appear on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent malfunction of the trailer brake system can cause the brakes to "buck" and "grab" when braking, which can lead to loss of control, accidents, or collisions.
symptoms: error messages related to braking wire malfunction appear on the dashboard
intermittent loss of trailer brake function.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Engine Stalling and Unintended Vehicle Fires
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine stalling and unintended vehicle fires can cause a loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of accidents, and pose a significant threat to the safety of occupants and bystanders.
symptoms: smoke is visible from the hood

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended opening of the tailgate can cause the payload to fall out, leading to accidents, damage to the towed vehicle or trailer, and hazards on the roadway.
symptoms: potential damage to towed vehicle or trailer

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The faulty tailgate latch design can cause the tailgate to open unexpectedly, leading to accidents, damage to the towed vehicle or trailer, and hazards on the roadway.
symptoms: potential damage to towed vehicle or trailer
